imdb.plot outline: Who?Mag TV takes you deep inside the entertainment industry and up close and personal with todays biggest urban celebrities ranging form Pitbull, Big Sean, Wyclef, Lil Jon, George Clinton, Public Enemy, to stars like Faizon Love, Shawn Alexander, Bernard Hopkins, and hundreds more. Let Who?Mag TV also introduce you to the stars of tomorrow first with their "Who?s Next" section, indie artist music video spotlights, as well as dazzle you with todays biggest names in exclusive live performances.
imdb.title: Who?Mag TV
plot: _Who?Mag TV_ (qv) is the largest independent international urban TV show focusing on hip-hop and R&B music with A-list interviews, concerts, music videos, and more. _Who?Mag TV_ (qv) has aired on 18 network.::David Loredo
